title: Rocket to the Moon
description: Rocket to the Moon is an uplifting story about using your imagination. Toby loves rocket ships and dreams of going to the moon one day. He turns to his father to find out if it would ever be possible for him to get to the moon. Follow Toby as he journey's to the moon using his imagination, with the help of his parents and his little sister Kayla.ROCKET TO THE MOON ISBN: 978-1-4568-2460-0Click this link to watch the book trailer for "Rocket to the Moon" http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TzxHmY...
author: Kelli Sullivan
